---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "@/components/Hero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Luxesur | Local Service Information, Solar, Roofing, Plumbing & More"
  description="Luxesur is a localized consumer information and request platform connecting property owners with service-related options across solar, roofing, plumbing, windows, and other home service categories."
>
  <Hero
    src="/images/home/home-hero.webp"
    alt="Localized home service information across solar, roofing, plumbing, and other property service categories"
  />

  <h1>Luxesur</h1>

  <p>
    Luxesur is a consumer-facing informational and request platform built to help
    property owners explore service-related options across localized markets.
    The platform is designed around city- and suburb-specific service pages that
    help consumers review information and submit requests based on location,
    service type, and availability.
  </p>

  <p>
    Luxesur currently supports localized content across emergency plumbing,
    solar, roofing, windows, and other home-related service categories as the
    platform continues to expand coverage. Service availability may vary by
    location, vertical, and active provider coverage.
  </p>

  <p>
    Luxesur does not directly perform repairs, installations, inspections, or
    emergency response. Services referenced on this website may be performed by
    independent third-party providers, affiliates, or service partners who are
    not employed, supervised, or controlled by Luxesur.
  </p>

  <p>
    Consumers may use this website to review local service information, explore
    available categories, and submit requests for follow-up based on service
    type, language, property details, and geographic relevance.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Available Service Categories</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/en/solar/quote/">Solar Information & Quote Requests</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/roofing/quote/">Roofing Information & Quote Requests</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/windows/quote/">Window Replacement Quote Requests</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/houston/">Emergency Plumbing Information</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>How the Platform Works</h2>

    <p>
      Luxesur publishes localized service-related informational pages across
      cities, suburbs, and service categories. Depending on the vertical,
      consumers may be able to request information, submit quote inquiries, or
      review time-sensitive service information related to specific property
      needs.
    </p>

    <p>
      Request and referral availability may depend on service category, property
      type, location, active provider coverage, and language support.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Business & Partner Contact</h2>

    <p>
      Service providers, buyers, affiliates, and business partners interested in
      working with Luxesur may contact us using the details below.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Main Business Line:</strong>
      <a href="tel:18665354699">1-866-535-4699</a>
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Email:</strong>
      <a href="mailto:partners@luxesur.com">partners@luxesur.com</a>
    </p>

    <p>
      These contact details are intended for business inquiries only and are not
      emergency service lines.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Service Areas</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/new-york/">New York</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/los-angeles/">Los Angeles</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/chicago/">Chicago</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/houston/">Houston</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/phoenix/">Phoenix</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/dallas/">Dallas</a></li>
      <li><a href="/en/emergency-plumbing/miami/">Miami</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>